room_title: Escape room "CSI: Coastal Bend" by 11th Hour Escape in Corpus Christi
room_address: 4455 S Padre Island Dr #105, Corpus Christi, TX 78411
room_description: Shots fired! Shots fired… at the hideout of the Coastal Bend’s most notorious crime boss. There’s a shooter on the loose but the murder weapon was left behind. You are the new Crime Scene Investigation team and all eyes are on you! You have 60 minutes to crack the case before they realize their mistake, return to the scene, and more shots are fired!
